奧倫?
Oren?

163
00:20:49,090 --> 00:20:51,718
我越來越擔心你了，奧倫
你太走極端
I'm getting worried about you, Oren.
This edge you've taken.

164
00:20:51,827 --> 00:20:53,658
這麼做對我們沒什麼好處
Displays like that aren't helpful to us.

165
00:20:53,762 --> 00:20:56,856
我堅決要保護我們所創造的世界
我不會為此道歉的
I believe in protecting what we've
created. I won't apologize for that.

166
00:20:56,965 --> 00:20:59,433
創造它是為了容許我
完成我的工作
This was created
to allow me to do my work.

167
00:20:59,768 --> 00:21:02,737
如果你不能控制自己
那我將無法完成
I can't do that
if you can't control yourself.

168
00:21:04,206 --> 00:21:06,037
- 我能理解
- 真的嗎?
- Understood.
- Is it?

169
00:21:07,242 --> 00:21:08,209
是的
Yes.

170
00:21:10,445 --> 00:21:13,676
- 試驗結果如何?
- 全盤失敗
- And what about the test results?
- All negative.

171
00:21:16,818 --> 00:21:17,876
抱歉
Sorry.

172
00:21:18,353 --> 00:21:20,287
今上午再給我
組建一個新的實驗團隊
Find me a new test group by morning.

173
00:21:21,323 --> 00:21:24,019
也許是時候放棄試驗了，特雷弗
Maybe it's time
to give up on the tests, Trevor.

174
00:21:24,826 --> 00:21:27,818
現有的解決方案已能讓我們生存
它是完美的
We're living the solution already.
This is perfection.

175
00:21:27,929 --> 00:21:31,228
- 為什麼你不能適可而止呢?
- 你注意到人們的行為舉止了吧
- Why can't you just embrace it?
- You see what's happening to people.

176
00:21:31,333 --> 00:21:33,062
你知道這多麼讓人絕望
You know
how desperate this has become.

177
00:21:33,168 --> 00:21:35,728
可它能被包容，被控制
It can be contained. Controlled.

178
00:21:36,271 --> 00:21:39,604
我認為你已經忘卻了
所有這些都是暫時性的
I think you're forgetting
that this was all meant to be temporary.

179
00:21:40,041 --> 00:21:42,509
我們總是那麼說，可為什麼呢?
We've always said that,
but why should it be?

180
00:21:42,611 --> 00:21:43,976
因為那是錯誤的
Because it's wrong.

181
00:21:44,312 --> 00:21:45,906
時代變了
Things change.

182
00:21:47,115 --> 00:21:48,412
但我知道你不會的
But I know you won't.

183
00:21:49,484 --> 00:21:50,644
你瞭解我的
You know me.

184
00:21:51,253 --> 00:21:53,177
我們可是幾百年的兄弟了
I've been your brother a long time.

185
00:21:53,555 --> 00:21:54,988
這你倒是說得對
You're right about that.

186
00:21:55,090 --> 00:21:56,819
特雷弗, 該去演講了
Trevor, your speech.

187
00:21:59,227 --> 00:22:00,455
特雷弗
Trevor...

188
00:22:19,514 --> 00:22:20,708
沒用了
Useless.

189
00:22:36,631 --> 00:22:39,065
- 確定目的地
- 論壇
- State destination,
- Forum.

190
00:22:40,502 --> 00:22:42,060
徑直向前
Proceed forward,

191
00:22:47,709 --> 00:22:49,472
轉向左
Proceed left,

192
00:22:51,613 --> 00:22:53,444
我知道你們心懷恐懼
I know you have fears,

193
00:22:53,915 --> 00:22:57,715
充滿悲傷，這動搖了你們的信念
磨煉你們的耐心
You have sorrows that shake your belief
and try your patience,

194
00:22:58,486 --> 00:23:01,046
但是現在非同以往
我們必須團結在一起
But now more than ever,
we must stand together,,,

195
00:23:01,156 --> 00:23:03,283
因為我們中間有股力量
because there are those among us,,,

196
00:23:03,391 --> 00:23:05,951
妄圖摧毀我們所創造的一切
who would tear down
what we have built,

197
00:23:06,361 --> 00:23:08,693
魔力黨人試圖分裂我們
The Monicans seek to divide us,

198
00:23:08,863 --> 00:23:11,093
我們決不能忘記我們是誰
We must never forget who we are,,,

199
00:23:11,199 --> 00:23:14,100
一個孤獨的部落，微不足道的組織
a lonely outpost, a tiny band,

200
00:23:14,869 --> 00:23:18,396
我們是一度覆蓋地球表面的
人類倖存者
We're all that remains of a people
that once covered the Earth.

201
00:23:18,673 --> 00:23:21,369
我們必須要適應新的挑戰
We must adapt together
to these new challenges.

202
00:23:22,344 --> 00:23:26,713
記住我們曾經面對的
倖免於難的瘟疫
Remember what we have faced,
what we have survived.

203
00:23:27,616 --> 00:23:29,083
我們會適應的
We will adapt.

204
00:23:32,921 --> 00:23:34,855
我們總是能夠適應的
We have always adapted.

205
00:23:42,197 --> 00:23:44,563
我們是一個有機的整體
It's the fabric of who we are.

206
00:23:54,676 --> 00:23:56,041
凱瑟琳
Katherine.

207
00:24:10,358 --> 00:24:11,586
是你啊
It's you.

208
00:24:29,811 --> 00:24:31,108
凱瑟琳
Katherine,

209
00:25:22,564 --> 00:25:23,997
等在外面
Wait outside.

210
00:25:36,177 --> 00:25:37,269
伊恩
Aeon.

211
00:25:38,179 --> 00:25:40,272
你早先叫我另外一個名字
You called me by another name earlier.

212
00:25:40,381 --> 00:25:43,111
是的，而你放了我一條生路
I did, and you let me live.

213
00:25:43,284 --> 00:25:46,515
給我槍，我們再來試過
Give me my gun. We'll try it again.

214
00:25:46,855 --> 00:25:48,447
下次再說吧
Maybe later.

215
00:25:50,058 --> 00:25:51,787
那名字什麼意思?
What was that name?

216
00:25:53,795 --> 00:25:55,660
你認識我，對嗎?
You know me, don't you?

217
00:25:56,664 --> 00:25:57,653
不
No.

218
00:25:58,633 --> 00:26:00,430
你知道自己是誰嗎?
Do you know who you are?

219
00:26:01,269 --> 00:26:04,796
- 我只知道我要來殺你
- 所以你才會被關起來
- I know I came here to kill you.
- That's why you're in a cell.

220
00:26:06,775 --> 00:26:09,505
但我們都為一個原因存活了下來
But we're both still alive for a reason.

221
00:26:14,949 --> 00:26:16,917
雖然不知道那是什麼
I don't know what this is...

222
00:26:19,621 --> 00:26:21,714
但見到你感覺真好
but it's good to see you.

223
00:26:59,360 --> 00:27:00,759
業餘水平
Amateurs.

224
00:28:08,329 --> 00:28:09,626
好小子
Good boys.

225
00:28:43,131 --> 00:28:45,326
- 伊恩
- 現在有點忙，西珊卓
- Aeon,
- Little busy, Sithandra.

226
00:28:45,433 --> 00:28:46,764
搞定了嗎?
Is it done?

227
00:28:48,603 --> 00:28:50,195
我需要更多時間
I need more time.

228
00:28:50,605 --> 00:28:52,436
我們收集的關於他的情報
也許是錯誤的
Our information on him may be wrong.

229
00:28:52,540 --> 00:28:55,668
我不想知道，我們必須行動
希望你...
I don't understand this,
We have to move, I hope you...

230
00:28:55,777 --> 00:28:57,972
別質疑我，西珊卓
Don't question me, Sithandra.

231
00:28:59,814 --> 00:29:01,111
我一會兒再聯絡你
I'll contact you soon.

232
00:29:01,215 --> 00:29:04,048
伊恩，你知道這麼做後果如何
Aeon, you know
there will be consequences to this,

233
00:29:04,252 --> 00:29:06,083
我知道我在做什麼
I know what I'm doing.

234
00:29:08,856 --> 00:29:09,982
真讓人難以容忍
This is outrageous.

235
00:29:10,091 --> 00:29:12,218
一個魔力黨人居然
避開了我們的全部設防?
One Monican
eluding all of our defenses?

236
00:29:12,327 --> 00:29:13,726
這個問題會被解決的
The problem will be taken care of.

237
00:29:13,828 --> 00:29:16,126
問題出在特雷弗的安全防範構想
The problem is
Trevor's concept of security.

238
00:29:16,230 --> 00:29:18,289
他必須要學會接受更為傳統的...
He needs to learn to accept
more traditional...

239
00:29:18,399 --> 00:29:20,663
要學會認可我們的投入
He needs to learn to accept our input.

240
00:29:20,902 --> 00:29:23,871
還有，就是他總是按自己的議程
自行其是，不管我們怎麼想
Another example of him pursuing his
own agenda, no matter what we think.

241
00:29:23,972 --> 00:29:26,805
- 我也開始懷疑他的議事日程了
- 什麼意思?
- I'm beginning to question his agenda.
- Meaning?

242
00:29:26,908 --> 00:29:29,536
那個魔力女殺手想要幹掉他
而他卻放她一馬?
The Monican tries to kill him
and he lets her live?

243
00:29:29,644 --> 00:29:31,077
這個決定非比尋常
An unusual choice.

244
00:29:31,679 --> 00:29:33,146
而現在她逃走了
And now she's escaped.

245
00:29:33,247 --> 00:29:34,908
有人相信這只是巧合嗎?
Does anyone believe
this is a coincidence?

246
00:29:35,016 --> 00:29:36,847
你們真的以為我只是一個應聲蟲
Do you really think
that I'm a sympathetic ear...

247
00:29:36,951 --> 00:29:39,010
只會聽你們對特雷弗發牢騷嗎?
for your complaints about Trevor?

248
00:29:40,188 --> 00:29:42,986
我們無權懷疑他的所作所為
You don't have the right
to question what he does.

249
00:29:43,091 --> 00:29:45,184
你得關注此事，奧倫
You must be concerned, Oren.

250
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,752
這可有違常規
This is hardly routine.

251
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:51,123
我認為我得和特雷弗談談
I think I should talk with Trevor.

252
00:29:51,366 --> 00:29:54,130
而你們大家都應該
更加謹慎行事
And I think
all of you should be more discreet.

253
00:29:56,938 --> 00:29:58,064
伊娜瑞?
Inari?

254
00:30:02,143 --> 00:30:04,202
圖像重建開始
Lmage retrieval commencing,

255
00:30:04,846 --> 00:30:06,108
這是怎麼回事?
What happened?

256
00:30:06,347 --> 00:30:07,905
我的原始數據對此沒有記錄
My sources were clear on this.

257
00:30:08,016 --> 00:30:10,143
伊恩·弗拉科斯是魔力黨的頂尖殺手
Aeon Flux
is the best the Monicans have.

258
00:30:10,251 --> 00:30:12,947
- 她失手了
- 這是她第一次失手
- She failed.
- It's the first time she has.

259
00:30:13,755 --> 00:30:15,518
我想要做的乾淨利落
I wanted this done cleanly.

260
00:30:16,524 --> 00:30:19,288
- 我的哥哥...
- 會比較容易受到傷害
- My brother...
- Will be vulnerable.

261
00:30:20,461 --> 00:30:21,860
準備演講...
Preparing his speech...

262
00:30:21,963 --> 00:30:24,022
明天，在1300坐標處...
Tomorrow, 1300...

263
00:30:26,434 --> 00:30:28,595
無論如何都追查不到你
It can't be traced to you, in any case.

264
00:30:28,836 --> 00:30:30,303
這還算令人寬慰
That's comforting.

265
00:30:30,905 --> 00:30:32,395
我們每件事都做得順遂
We did everything correctly.

266
00:30:32,507 --> 00:30:35,135
- 她有機會的
- 可她沒下手
- She had her opportunity.
- And she stopped.

267
00:30:35,576 --> 00:30:36,736
為什麼?
Why?

268
00:30:38,646 --> 00:30:41,740
- 我也不知道
- 圖像重建進行中
- I don't know.
- Image retrieval underway,

269
00:30:42,050 --> 00:30:44,348
發起另一次襲擊太過冒險
lt'll be too risky to call another hit.

270
00:30:44,452 --> 00:30:47,319
魔力黨人會懷疑自己受到利用
The Monicans may suspect
they are being used.

271
00:30:50,958 --> 00:30:52,118
暫停
Stop.

272
00:30:54,429 --> 00:30:55,487
奧倫?
Oren?

273
00:30:56,497 --> 00:30:57,486
不
No.

274
00:30:59,434 --> 00:31:01,061
那不可能
That's impossible.

275
00:31:14,248 --> 00:31:15,374
克勞迪斯
Claudius.

276
00:31:17,685 --> 00:31:21,121
- 你怎麼還在這裡?
- 不是你想的那麼簡單
- Why are you still here?
- It's not as simple as you think.

277
00:31:21,656 --> 00:31:24,750
烏娜被殺害了
而你居然還在為兇手工作?
Una is murdered and you keep working
for the people who did it?

278
00:31:24,859 --> 00:31:26,986
- 你說我會怎麼想?
- 你不明白的
- What should I be thinking?
- You don't know.

279
00:31:27,095 --> 00:31:28,892
我怎麼不明白?
What don't I know?

280
00:31:29,530 --> 00:31:31,054
他們殺害了她
They killed her.

281
00:31:31,632 --> 00:31:34,294
- 而你依然苟且偷生
- 是你害了她，伊恩
- And you're still alive.
- You killed her, Aeon.

282
00:31:34,702 --> 00:31:37,569
他們認為她是魔力黨人
所以她才會遇害
They thought she was a Monican,
that's why she died.

283
00:31:38,806 --> 00:31:42,139
- 烏娜的生命本不至如此
- 她是我的全部
- Una's life was won'th more than that.
- She was all I had.

284
00:31:44,145 --> 00:31:45,806
不是只有你這麼想
You're not the only one.

285
00:31:48,716 --> 00:31:51,412
你究竟在這裡做什麼，克勞迪斯?
What are you
really doing here, Claudius?

286
00:31:52,420 --> 00:31:53,614
工作
Working.

287
00:31:54,989 --> 00:31:56,684
剩下的只有工作了
It's all that's left.

288
00:31:56,791 --> 00:31:59,157
工作，為了特雷弗·古德查德
Working. For Trevor Goodchild.

289
00:32:00,695 --> 00:32:02,322
我也詛咒他
I blamed him, too.

290
00:32:02,430 --> 00:32:04,694
可是現在，我覺得不是特雷弗的錯
But now
I don't think it was Trevor's fault.

291
00:32:04,799 --> 00:32:06,562
特雷弗在努力嘗試
Trevor's trying to help.

292
00:32:06,667 --> 00:32:10,626
我們都不太對勁，伊恩
所有人都是
Something is wrong with us, Aeon.
With everybody.

293
00:32:11,839 --> 00:32:14,103
你也做夢的，對吧?
You have the dreams, don't you?

294
00:32:14,375 --> 00:32:17,037
回想起一些從不屬於你的事情?
Memories of things
that never happened to you?

295
00:32:17,145 --> 00:32:19,409
烏娜是這樣，我也是
Una had them. I have them.

296
00:32:19,514 --> 00:32:21,573
布瑞格拉全城都是這樣
It's happening all across Bregna.

297
00:32:21,682 --> 00:32:23,741
- 這是怎麼回事?
- 我也不知道
- What is it?
- I don't know.

298
00:32:23,985 --> 00:32:26,453
他們只告訴我們需要知道的
They only tell us what we need to know.

299
00:32:26,554 --> 00:32:29,182
我的工作僅僅是一個更大實驗的
微小組成部分
My work is a small part
of a larger experiment.

300
00:32:29,290 --> 00:32:31,724
- 誰的實驗?
- 特雷弗的
- Whose experiment?
- Trevor's.

301
00:32:32,493 --> 00:32:35,519
我們正在研究圍城外部世界的事物
We're studying
what's growing outside the wall.

302
00:32:35,997 --> 00:32:39,433
我們治癒工業瘟疫的同時
又催生了新的事物
Something happened
when they cured the industrial disease.

303
00:32:39,534 --> 00:32:42,128
其他隱患又產生了
Something else sprung up in its place.

304
00:32:42,870 --> 00:32:44,201
我們都出現了病態
We're sick.

305
00:32:45,139 --> 00:32:48,302
特雷弗試圖治癒我們
我就知道這些
And Trevor's trying to cure us.
That's all I know.

306
00:32:53,080 --> 00:32:54,707
特雷弗想要給我下藥
Trevor tried to dope me.

307
00:32:55,049 --> 00:32:56,641
告訴我這是什麼
Tell me what's in this.

308
00:33:04,091 --> 00:33:05,581
是條信息
It's a message.

309
00:33:06,093 --> 00:33:07,651
哦，那它說什麼?
Well, what does it say?

310
00:33:08,296 --> 00:33:11,060
你必須先喝下去
然後它才會起效
You have to drink it.
That's how it works.

311
00:33:15,369 --> 00:33:16,734
我愛她
I loved her.

312
00:33:20,141 --> 00:33:21,608
你知道的
You know that.

313
00:33:41,762 --> 00:33:42,820
伊恩
Aeon,

314
00:33:44,165 --> 00:33:48,295
我很抱歉這引起的不適
但公開場合講話不太安全
I'm sorry for the pain,
but it's not safe to talk in the open,

315
00:33:49,337 --> 00:33:51,464
凡事往往表裡不一
Nothing is as it seems,

316
00:33:53,874 --> 00:33:56,741
既然你有機會，為什麼要猶豫?
You had your chance,
Why did you hesitate?

317
00:34:00,781 --> 00:34:02,476
你知道該去哪裡找我
You know where to find me,

318
00:34:31,412 --> 00:34:34,939
- 為什麼我會來這裡?
- 因為我想要再見到你
- Why am I here?
- I needed to see you again.

319
00:34:35,716 --> 00:34:37,479
你殺害了我妹妹
You killed my sister.

320
00:34:38,085 --> 00:34:40,053
我對此一無所知
I didn't know anything about it.

321
00:34:40,888 --> 00:34:42,082
對不起
I'm sorry.

322
00:34:42,290 --> 00:34:44,383
- 這就是你的托辭?
- 不是
- And that excuses you?
- No.

323
00:34:44,625 --> 00:34:47,423
可這是戰爭，各方都有死傷
But this is a war.
People on all sides die.

324
00:34:47,862 --> 00:34:51,127
但她不應該，她與此毫無瓜葛
She shouldn't have.
She had nothing to do with this.

325
00:34:52,033 --> 00:34:55,332
- 人人都牽連其中
- 可是她沒有
- Everyone is involved in this.
- She wasrt.

326
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:01,440
我殺你用不著這個
I don't need that to kill you.

