00:57:32,240 --> 00:57:36,233
現在，當一個人死後
其DNA會重複利用
Now, when a person dies,
their DNA is recycled.

500
00:57:36,378 --> 00:57:39,370
奧倫和我建造了空中遺跡
用來儲存DNA
Oren and I built the Relical
to store the DNA,,,

501
00:57:39,481 --> 00:57:41,449
並對克隆程序加以保密
and conceal the cloning process,

502
00:57:41,850 --> 00:57:44,546
由保管人尋找條件適合的夫婦
The Keeper finds a suitable couple,,,

503
00:57:45,153 --> 00:57:48,748
然後利用食品添加劑
導致藥物受孕
and, using food additives,
we induce a chemical pregnancy,

504
00:57:50,525 --> 00:57:54,484
當婦女來體檢時，再植入克隆胚胎
When the woman comes in for an exam,
we implant a cloned embryo,

505
00:57:54,896 --> 00:57:57,023
從那時起，一切變得自然而然
From there, things happen naturally.

506
00:57:57,566 --> 00:58:01,366
9個月以後，死去的市民得以重生
In nine months,
a citizen who died is reborn,

507
00:58:03,772 --> 00:58:07,208
已經繁衍了7代人
奧倫和我也克隆了我們自己
For seven generations,
Oren and I have cloned ourselves,,,

508
00:58:07,309 --> 00:58:11,143
也教會我們自己
使我得以繼續探尋祛病之道...
taught ourselves, so that
I could keep trying to find a cure,,,

509
00:58:13,115 --> 00:58:14,912
同時延續著生命
while we all live on,

510
00:58:19,821 --> 00:58:21,550
我們就只是那樣嗎?
That's what we are?

511
00:58:22,758 --> 00:58:23,918
複製品?
Copies?

512
00:58:25,127 --> 00:58:26,890
我們並不滿足於此
We're more than that.

513
00:58:30,932 --> 00:58:33,400
那並非長久之計
It wasrt supposed to be permanent.

514
00:58:36,405 --> 00:58:39,203
我試圖治療不育症
I've been trying to cure the infertility.

515
00:58:42,511 --> 00:58:45,105
烏娜是我試驗組中的一員
Una was part of one of my test groups.

516
00:58:45,781 --> 00:58:47,339
奧倫對我撒了謊
Oren lied to me.

517
00:58:47,649 --> 00:58:50,675
他告訴我她的試驗
像其他人一樣失敗了
He told me her test had failed
like the others.

518
00:58:51,420 --> 00:58:53,513
但是她懷孕了
But she had become pregnant.

519
00:58:56,825 --> 00:58:59,123
他殺害了所有受試者
He killed all of the subjects.

520
00:58:59,995 --> 00:59:01,758
包括你妹妹
Your sister included.

521
00:59:04,433 --> 00:59:07,061
因為她懷了孕，所以要殺她
He killed her
because she was pregnant.

522
00:59:12,140 --> 00:59:13,835
烏娜並不知道這些...
Una didn't know it...

523
00:59:14,443 --> 00:59:18,675
但她的孩子本該是400年來
第一個新出生的嬰兒
but her baby would've been one
of the first new children in 400 years.

524
00:59:20,849 --> 00:59:22,339
是奧倫改變了這些
Orers changed.

525
00:59:23,919 --> 00:59:27,150
他不想回到過去
也不想有祛病之策
He doesn't want to go back.
He doesn't want a cure.

526
00:59:28,090 --> 00:59:30,058
他想要永生
He wants to live forever.

527
00:59:39,496 --> 00:59:43,159
既然你有膽幫助魔力黨人
一定也想過會這樣吧?
You must've been expecting this
after helping that Monican.

528
00:59:45,669 --> 00:59:48,797
你對特雷弗的忠誠
再也保護不了你了
Your loyalty to Trevor
can't protect you anymore.

529
00:59:48,939 --> 00:59:51,965
我所忠誠的比這要深刻許多
I'm loyal to something deeper
than any of this.

530
00:59:52,976 --> 00:59:55,638
我搞不懂像你和特雷弗那樣的人
I don't understand
people like you and Trevor.

531
00:59:55,746 --> 01:00:01,564
你們的優柔寡斷
對陳年往事的念念不忘
Your sentimentality,
your devotion to the past...
to things that are gone.

532
01:00:01,652 --> 01:00:04,212
沒有那些我將無法生存
I couldn't live without those things.

533
01:00:04,955 --> 01:00:06,320
你怎麼能...？
How can you?

534
01:00:24,541 --> 01:00:25,667
薩莎
Sasha.

535
01:00:27,177 --> 01:00:30,510
我們該走了
奧倫用不了多久就會找到我們的
We should go.
It won't take long for Oren to find us.

536
01:00:34,852 --> 01:00:36,820
她很快就會活蹦亂跳了
She's gonna be a handful.

537
01:00:40,757 --> 01:00:42,281
快走，他們要找的不是你們
Go. They don't want you.

538
01:00:42,392 --> 01:00:43,416
快走!
Go!

539
01:03:41,471 --> 01:03:42,597
趴下!
Down!

540
01:03:59,089 --> 01:04:01,319
不，你得保持清醒
No. You need to stay conscious.

541
01:04:10,567 --> 01:04:12,194
請保持平靜
Please remain calm,

542
01:04:13,170 --> 01:04:15,968
我們遇到了技術故障
We are experiencing
a technical malfunction,

543
01:04:18,742 --> 01:04:20,471
請保持平靜
Please remain calm,

544
01:04:21,345 --> 01:04:24,246
我們遇到了技術故障
We are experiencing
a technical malfunction,

545
01:04:25,782 --> 01:04:27,647
請保持平靜
Please remain calm,

546
01:04:28,285 --> 01:04:30,219
我們遇到了...
We are experiencing,,,,

547
01:04:41,932 --> 01:04:44,423
我們不能去魔力黨藏身處
We can't go to a Monican safe house.

548
01:04:44,634 --> 01:04:46,898
對我們來說，沒有地方是安全的
Nowhere's going to be safe for us.

549
01:05:02,819 --> 01:05:05,083
我們得把子彈取出來
We need to get the bullets out.

550
01:05:42,459 --> 01:05:44,450
還有其它地方受傷嗎？
Are you hit anywhere else?

551
01:05:49,666 --> 01:05:52,157
他們當中有誰想要放過你嗎？
Did any of them manage to miss you?

552
01:06:11,655 --> 01:06:14,215
或許我們該去圍牆外面
We might have to go outside the wall.

553
01:06:15,459 --> 01:06:16,619
我知道
I know.

554
01:06:19,496 --> 01:06:21,487
首先，我必須終結這一切
First, I have to end this.

555
01:06:25,335 --> 01:06:27,132
我得回去一趟
I need to go back in.

556
01:06:27,404 --> 01:06:30,305
我要拿回烏娜試驗組的資料
I have to get my notes
from Una's test group.

557
01:06:30,974 --> 01:06:35,274
奧倫會找到實驗室
破壞我所有的成果
Oren will find the lab and destroy it,
everything I've done.

558
01:06:51,027 --> 01:06:53,552
所有軍事單位向駐地匯報...
All military units should report
to their stations,,,

559
01:06:53,663 --> 01:06:55,756
並等待進一步指令
and wait for further instructions,

560
01:07:03,139 --> 01:07:04,936
誰負責這裡？
Who's in charge here?

561
01:07:06,343 --> 01:07:07,708
我們需要你們的幫助
We need your help.

562
01:07:07,811 --> 01:07:10,336
- 我們得到命令，見到你就開槍
- 這是政變
- We have orders to shoot you on sight.
- There's been a coup.

563
01:07:10,447 --> 01:07:13,211
你們的命令來自於非法政府
Your orders are coming
from an illegitimate government.

564
01:07:13,316 --> 01:07:16,183
- 站住別動，長官!
- 你叫什麼名字?
- Stay where you are, sir!
- What's your name?

565
01:07:16,653 --> 01:07:18,883
- 長官?
- 我想知道你的名字
- Sir?
- I want to know your name.

566
01:07:20,390 --> 01:07:22,984
我叫奧德，加萊特·奧德
It's Ord. Garret Ord.

567
01:07:23,527 --> 01:07:27,122
我再也不能命令你了，加萊特
但他們同樣不能
I can't command you anymore, Garret.
But neither can they.

568
01:07:27,697 --> 01:07:29,130
你是自由人了
You're free.

569
01:07:29,933 --> 01:07:32,060
你必須做出決定
You need to make a decision.

570
01:07:35,539 --> 01:07:38,235
無論開槍還是幫助我們
請你快些決斷
Shoot us or help us, but do it quickly.

571
01:07:39,676 --> 01:07:41,007
中尉？
Lieutenant?

572
01:07:49,452 --> 01:07:52,046
該怎樣做才能幫到你
古德查德主席?
How can I help you,
Chairman Goodchild?

573
01:07:55,425 --> 01:07:58,189
我們需要武器，重返大本營
We need weapons.
We need to get back into the Citadel.

574
01:07:58,295 --> 01:07:59,523
是，長官
Yes, sir.

575
01:08:09,639 --> 01:08:13,598
注意，請返回崗位
並等待進一步指令
Attention, Please return to your home
and wait for further instructions,

576
01:08:13,710 --> 01:08:15,405
新指令將不斷下達
You will be updated frequently,

577
01:08:15,512 --> 01:08:19,539
這是參議會和奧倫·古德查德主席
發佈的通告
This is an announcement from the
Council and Chairman Oren Goodchild,

578
01:08:21,651 --> 01:08:25,815
注意，請返回崗位
並等待進一步指令
Attention, Please return to your home
and wait for further instructions,

579
01:08:29,826 --> 01:08:31,919
- 我們接近目的地了
- 等一下
- We're getting closer.
- Wait.

580
01:08:51,915 --> 01:08:53,143
特雷弗
Trevor.

581
01:08:55,485 --> 01:08:57,476
你叫過我的名字...
The name you called me...

582
01:09:00,390 --> 01:09:01,687
凱瑟琳
Katherine.

583
01:09:02,959 --> 01:09:04,551
我以前叫這個名字
That was my name.

584
01:09:08,131 --> 01:09:09,723
你曾是我的妻子
You were my wife.

585
01:09:14,304 --> 01:09:17,330
我們以前一起生活
就像其他人一樣
We had a life together,
just like anybody else.

586
01:09:17,807 --> 01:09:18,865
等一下
Wait.

587
01:09:20,176 --> 01:09:21,905
你必須告訴我詳情
You need to tell me.

588
01:09:24,080 --> 01:09:28,016
在瘟疫期間我失去了你
因為沒辦法治好你
I lost you during the disease,
and you couldn't be brought back.

589
01:09:28,585 --> 01:09:31,679
從那之後我出生並死亡了7次
I've lived and died
seven times since then.

590
01:09:33,456 --> 01:09:36,118
每次我都告訴自己關於你的事
And each time
I taught myself about you,

591
01:09:36,926 --> 01:09:39,121
你是讓我活下去的信念所在
You were an idea I kept alive.

592
01:09:39,629 --> 01:09:41,688
有些事我只能靠自己想像
Something I had to imagine.

593
01:09:46,903 --> 01:09:48,666
但自從見到你
But when I saw you...

594
01:09:51,541 --> 01:09:53,338
我所感覺的才變得真實
what I felt was real.

595
01:09:54,244 --> 01:09:55,609
我認識你的
I knew you.

596
01:09:57,447 --> 01:09:59,039
我想起你來了
I remembered you.

597
01:09:59,582 --> 01:10:03,518
存留在我們心中的感情
超越了死亡，超越了萬物
What we had then survived in us
past death, past everything.

598
01:10:05,789 --> 01:10:07,620
我一直在找尋你
I was looking for you.

599
01:10:08,892 --> 01:10:10,519
而我一直在等待
I've been waiting.

600
01:10:12,162 --> 01:10:14,130
我們曾是其他人
We were different people,

601
01:10:14,964 --> 01:10:16,158
我們曾經是
We were,

602
01:10:16,966 --> 01:10:18,695
雖然那些人已經逝去
Those people are gone,

603
01:10:20,503 --> 01:10:22,801
但卻以另一種方式重生了
But something in them came back.

604
01:10:24,074 --> 01:10:25,098
是的
Yes.

605
01:10:40,924 --> 01:10:42,255
我記起來了
I remember.

606
01:10:44,828 --> 01:10:46,591
外面的局勢非常混亂
It's chaos out there.

607
01:10:46,696 --> 01:10:48,664
有一場針對古德查德的政變
There's a coup against Goodchild.

608
01:10:48,765 --> 01:10:50,756
潛入更容易了
Made it easier to slip in.

609
01:10:50,934 --> 01:10:52,367
有辦法找到她嗎？
Did you bring a way to find her?

610
01:10:52,469 --> 01:10:55,529
只要有她體內藥丸存留的痕跡
就能追蹤到她
As long as there's a trace of the pill
in her, we can track her.

611
01:11:05,982 --> 01:11:07,006
不
No.

612
01:11:25,902 --> 01:11:27,062
弗雷娜
Freya.

613
01:11:33,276 --> 01:11:34,573
完了
It's gone.

614
01:11:36,813 --> 01:11:38,337
我所找到的祛病之策
I had cured it.

615
01:11:38,581 --> 01:11:40,481
我所發現的訣竅
I'd found the answer.

616
01:11:40,984 --> 01:11:42,451
全部付諸東流
It's all gone.

617
01:11:45,455 --> 01:11:47,320
我們還要繼續行動
We have to keep moving.

618
01:11:56,299 --> 01:11:58,767
還有一件事要做
There's still one more thing to do.

619
01:11:59,302 --> 01:12:03,102
沒什麼事要做了，我們得離開這裡
There's nothing left to do.
You and I need to get out of here.

620
01:12:04,107 --> 01:12:07,338
到圍牆外面去
我們會找到生存之道的
We go outside the wall.
We'll find a way to live.

621
01:12:07,443 --> 01:12:10,970
還有一件事要做
我要毀了它
There's one more thing to do.
I need to destroy it.

622
01:12:11,781 --> 01:12:12,770
不
No.

623
01:12:15,385 --> 01:12:17,046
這不是解決辦法，伊恩
This isn't the answer, Aeon.

624
01:12:17,153 --> 01:12:19,519
我無法保證
能再找到祛病良策
There's no guarantee
I can find the cure again.

625
01:12:19,622 --> 01:12:22,614
- 克隆是我們僅有的
- 可這還不夠
- The cloning is all we have.
- It's not enough.

626
01:12:23,193 --> 01:12:26,856
我們的心智已逐漸打開
每一次克隆都使情況變得更糟
Our minds are unraveling, and every
time you bring us back it gets worse.

627
01:12:26,963 --> 01:12:28,863
你這樣做意味著人類的終結
If you do this, we end.

628
01:12:29,365 --> 01:12:31,094
我們注定要死亡
We're meant to die.

629
01:12:32,669 --> 01:12:35,399
只有這樣，我們的存在才有意義
It's what makes
anything about us matter.

630
01:12:37,674 --> 01:12:39,733
這麼活著是一種煎熬
Living like this is torture.

631
01:12:39,843 --> 01:12:41,504
就像鬼魂一樣
We're just ghosts.

632
01:12:43,513 --> 01:12:45,140
我可沒有這樣的感覺
That's not how I feel.

633
01:12:47,417 --> 01:12:48,509
至少現在沒有
Not now.

634
01:12:56,626 --> 01:12:58,218
我們要多加小心
Let's be careful.

635
01:12:58,695 --> 01:13:00,925
大家要知道我們對抗的是誰
You know who we're up against.

636
01:13:07,337 --> 01:13:10,363
- 這樣做只是做做樣子罷了
- 但這是理念的飛躍
- This is an empty gesture.
- It's a leap of faith.

637
01:13:10,473 --> 01:13:12,532
這不是由你決定的
It's not for you to decide.

638
01:13:13,509 --> 01:13:17,001
伊恩，我不想再失去你
Aeon, I don't want to lose you again.

639
01:13:18,448 --> 01:13:20,109
你不必如此
You don't have to.

640
01:13:21,351 --> 01:13:23,410
你會再次發現解決之道的
You'll find the cure again.

641
01:13:24,787 --> 01:13:26,448
都結束了，特雷弗
It's over, Trevor.

642
01:13:34,163 --> 01:13:36,688
轉移到南部的塔尖
Moving into position on the south spire.

643
01:13:39,502 --> 01:13:42,096
已經有比你的治療
更有效的方法出現了
It goes so much deeper than your cure.

644
01:13:42,639 --> 01:13:45,301
有些婦女已經自然受孕了...
Other women have been
getting pregnant naturally...

645
01:13:45,408 --> 01:13:47,501
在你試驗之外
outside of your experiments.

646
01:13:47,710 --> 01:13:49,541
越來越多的人懷孕了
More and more of them.

647
01:13:50,680 --> 01:13:52,545
她們自發痊癒了
They healed themselves.

648
01:13:53,549 --> 01:13:56,450
- 你把她們也殺死了?
- 我必須阻止它
- And you killed them, too?
- I had to stop it.

649
01:13:57,353 --> 01:13:58,650
有多少人?
How many?

650
01:14:03,092 --> 01:14:04,320
多少人，奧倫?
How many, Oren?

651
01:14:05,061 --> 01:14:08,326
那無關緊要，自然之力
終於自尋出路了
It doesn't matter.
Nature's finally found a way.

652
01:14:11,634 --> 01:14:13,397
- 到達指定位置
- 到達指定位置
- In position.
- In position.

653
01:14:13,503 --> 01:14:14,834
指定位置已到達
Position acquired,

654
01:14:15,204 --> 01:14:18,139
該被淘汰的是自然，而不是我們
Nature's the one who's obsolete, not us.

655
01:14:19,409 --> 01:14:23,607
你為什麼還不明白
你所創造的美好奇跡? 我都明白
How can you not understand
the beauty of what you made? I do.

656
01:14:24,948 --> 01:14:26,609
情況越發複雜了
Situatiors getting complicated.

657
01:14:33,423 --> 01:14:35,550
你告訴我她已經死了
You told me she was gone.

658
01:14:40,063 --> 01:14:41,860
他們已經盡力而為了
There was nothing that they could do.

659
01:14:45,535 --> 01:14:47,662
我命令銷毀她的DNA
I ordered her DNA destroyed.

660
01:14:49,238 --> 01:14:51,638
和她在一起
讓你變成了另一個人，特雷弗
You were a different man
with her, Trevor.

661
01:14:51,741 --> 01:14:54,938
她會阻止你做你該做的事
She would've stopped you
from doing what needed to be done.

662
01:14:56,045 --> 01:14:57,945
- 就像她現在在阻止你一樣
- 不，奧倫
- Like she's stopping you now.
- No, Oren.

663
01:14:58,047 --> 01:14:59,071
是的
Yes.

664
01:14:59,415 --> 01:15:01,280
- 請下指令
- 等我信號
- Waiting for the go.
- On my signal.

665
01:15:01,384 --> 01:15:03,614
這個世界，我們的世界
已經很完美了
This world, our world, is beautiful.

666
01:15:04,253 --> 01:15:06,346
值得用任何代價來維護
Worth preserving at any cost.

667
01:15:06,489 --> 01:15:08,889
這不會長久的
它已經在分崩離析了
It can't last. It's falling apart.

668
01:15:12,795 --> 01:15:14,695
西珊卓，給我們信號
Sithandra, give us the signal,

669
01:15:16,666 --> 01:15:19,032
- 西珊卓
- 先放倒弗拉科斯
- Sithandra,
- Take Flux down first.

670
01:15:19,135 --> 01:15:20,227
你在這個問題上是錯的，奧倫
You're wrong in this, Oren.

671
01:15:20,336 --> 01:15:22,736
我們擊敗了死亡，擊敗了自然
We've beaten death, beaten nature.

672
01:15:23,940 --> 01:15:25,601
我們已經凌駕於你的構想
We've gone beyond you.

673
01:15:26,275 --> 01:15:28,300
現在我要擺脫你的束縛
And now I need to be free of you.

674
01:15:38,554 --> 01:15:39,612
等一下
Wait.

675
01:15:52,635 --> 01:15:53,966
西珊卓
Sithandra.

676
01:15:58,241 --> 01:16:01,005
這是你自食其果
伊恩，太遲了
You chose this, Aeon. It's too late.

677
01:16:01,377 --> 01:16:03,402
你知道我們所經受的苦楚
You know how much we're all suffering.

678
01:16:03,513 --> 01:16:05,879
我正在努力終結它，特雷弗也是
I'm trying to end it, and so is Trevor.

679
01:16:06,516 --> 01:16:08,450
我永遠不會背叛你
I would never betray you.

680
01:16:09,052 --> 01:16:10,246
幫幫我
Help me.

681
01:16:12,422 --> 01:16:13,753
西珊卓
Sithandra,

682
01:16:14,924 --> 01:16:16,585
你還是瞭解我的
You still know me,

683
01:16:16,692 --> 01:16:18,023
幹掉她
Finish it.

684
01:16:18,928 --> 01:16:20,987
你可以選擇信任我
You can choose to trust me,

685
01:16:25,835 --> 01:16:26,824
幹掉她
Finish it.

686
01:16:26,936 --> 01:16:28,528
對不起，奧倫
I'm sorry, Oren.

687
01:16:28,771 --> 01:16:29,829
對不起
I'm sorry.

688
01:16:29,939 --> 01:16:31,065
我也是
I am, too.

689
01:16:36,045 --> 01:16:39,242
更改命令，掩護伊恩
掩護古德查德
Orders have changed.
Cover Aeon. Cover Goodchild.

690
01:17:21,824 --> 01:17:23,121
古德查德被擊中了
Goodchild's been hit.

691
01:17:27,697 --> 01:17:29,358
弗拉科斯正在向庭院挺進
Flux is headed to the courtyard.

692
01:17:33,202 --> 01:17:34,533
掩護伊恩
Cover Aeon.

693
01:18:58,354 --> 01:18:59,685
西珊卓!
Sithandra!

694
01:19:50,940 --> 01:19:52,032
奧倫
Oren.

695
01:20:25,841 --> 01:20:27,331
他們來了
They're coming.

696
01:20:32,515 --> 01:20:33,675
伊恩
Aeon.

697
01:20:53,736 --> 01:20:55,931
我們在等待您的命令
We're waiting for your orders.

698
01:20:56,439 --> 01:20:58,373
你們沒份參與？
You're not part of this?

699
01:20:59,375 --> 01:21:01,969
不論是否參與
我們都不是無政府主義者
Whatever we are, we're not anarchists.

700
01:21:02,378 --> 01:21:04,869
- 必須要有規則
- 謝謝
- There have to be rules.
- Thank you.

701
01:21:36,946 --> 01:21:38,470
你就是那個人
You're the one.

702
01:21:39,248 --> 01:21:40,681
是你救了我
You saved me.

703
01:21:41,283 --> 01:21:42,307
不錯
Yes.

704
01:21:43,519 --> 01:21:45,077
我那時認識你
I knew you then,

705
01:21:45,454 --> 01:21:48,082
她的軀體已被侵蝕，毀掉她
This one was corrupted. Destroy it.

706
01:21:48,624 --> 01:21:50,615
我知道你很重要
I knew you were important.

707
01:21:51,293 --> 01:21:52,851
DNA是完好的
The DNA is good.

708
01:21:52,962 --> 01:21:54,293
毀掉她
Destroy it.

709
01:22:00,236 --> 01:22:02,761
我知道我該保護你
I knew that I needed to protect you,

710
01:22:04,573 --> 01:22:08,669
我將你的DNA儲存在休眠狀態
I kept your DNA hidden here, dormant.

711
01:22:09,311 --> 01:22:12,007
直到現在才讓你重生
I've waited until now to bring you back.

712
01:22:12,348 --> 01:22:13,372
為什麼？
Why?

713
01:22:13,682 --> 01:22:18,551
我知道你的力量會一併保存下來
I knew that your strength
would survive with you.

714
01:22:18,921 --> 01:22:22,721
如果讓你重生，你就可以改變特雷弗
I thought that if I brought you back,
you could reach Trevor.

715
01:22:24,160 --> 01:22:25,787
你一直擁有這種力量
You always could.

716
01:22:27,096 --> 01:22:30,031
- 我必須終結這一切
- 是的
- I have to end it.
- Yes.

717
01:22:31,133 --> 01:22:32,395
從頭再來
Start over.

718
01:22:33,269 --> 01:22:34,793
那你怎麼辦？
What about you?

719
01:22:36,739 --> 01:22:39,936
我等了400年，就是為了這天
I've waited 400 years for this day.

720
01:22:43,546 --> 01:22:44,843
我太累了
I'm tired.

721
01:22:52,354 --> 01:22:53,946
好好活下去，伊恩
Stay alive, Aeon.

722
01:22:56,125 --> 01:22:57,649
人民需要你
You are needed.

723
01:23:49,879 --> 01:23:51,107
看哪!
Look!

724
01:24:58,681 --> 01:25:00,672
現在我們可以大步向前了
Now we can move forward,,,

725
01:25:01,850 --> 01:25:05,286
真實地活上一生一世
to live once for real,,,

726
01:25:07,256 --> 01:25:12,955
然後把世界留給那些
能將它變得更美好的後代們
and then give way to people
who might do it better,

727
01:25:19,668 --> 01:25:21,397
嘿，凱瑟琳
Hey, Katherine.

728
01:25:25,174 --> 01:25:26,971
我能再見到你嗎？
Will I see you again?

729
01:25:37,686 --> 01:25:39,415
儘管人生只有一次...
To live only once,,,

730
01:25:44,727 --> 01:25:46,217
卻要活得充滿希望
but with hope,

731
01:25:50,217 --> 01:26:18,217
劇終  歡迎光臨
